column1: IF ccr_thf_d is MF 1 THEN 4_Obese is MF 1 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 0 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 1

IF cr_l8_oh_f_d is MF 2 AND ccr_pt_d is MF 1 THEN 2_Normal is MF 1 AND 4_Obese is MF 0 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 0
IF ccr_thb_d is MF 0 AND ccr_pt_d is MF 1 AND ccr_a_cortol_d is MF 0 THEN 3_Surpoid is MF 1 AND 5_ExtremeObese is MF 0
IF ccr_s_pt_d is MF 2 THEN 5_ExtremeObese is MF 1 AND 1_SousPoid is MF 0 AND 4_Obese is MF 0
